author: Daniel Greene
description:
🔥 In this episode: We delve into The Wheel of Time Season 3, Episode 6, titled "The Shadow in the Night." This ep brings a lot to the table including 
a musical performance with Elayne singing a performance of "The Hills of Tanchico." Moghedien shows us just how intimate someone can get with food. And Rand realizes there might be consequences to his actions.
